original_title: Flotsam and Jetsam Live in Japan
overview: Recorded live at Club Citta', Kawasaki, Japan 26 September 2004. Setlist: 01 - Me - 02 - No Place for Disgrace - 03 - The Master Sleeps - 04 - Nothing to Say - 05 - Hard on You - 06 - Escape From Within - 07 - Hammerhead - 08 - Doomsday for the Deceiver and the video for Straight to Hell
title: Flotsam and Jetsam Live in Japan
